				<td colspan="2"><span>Just curious - what are some good quests or 'miniraids' (termed so for the sense of adventure) for the 40s bard. Looking for things doable solo, or with a 3-6 person 40s group.  This is meant for those of us tired of mindlessly leveling or LDoN'ing - so looking for reward and challenge here - not exp- Thanks )
<br />

<br />
What I have done or thought of
<br />

<br />
- Clear Crystal Caverns (queen)
<br />
- Aria of Asceticism quest
<br />
- Burnoose of the Halfbreed - Jaggedpine
<br />
- Mask of Deception - Lower Guk
<br />
- Bag of Sewn Evil-Eye - Lower Guk
<br />
- Assist shaman with Stoicism quest
<br />
- Beginnings of epic
<br />

<br />
Lol my list draws short. Hopefully someone can add some!</span></td>
