				<td colspan="2"><span>Hmmm, no new suggestions here, just some feedback:
<br />

<br />
Aria of Asceticism quest may be too easy, and probably heavily camped.
<br />

<br />
Mask of Deception - Lower Guk WAY too easy.  Soloable in the upper 30s with decent gear.
<br />

<br />
Bag of Sewn Evil-Eye - Lower Guk  Even easier, soloable in mid 30s, with decent faction on Live Guk side.
<br />

<br />
Beginnings of epic  Highly advised.  Neze and Eldrig should be a good challenge, and not the easiest to find.  Having a group makes it all the better.  (note, still working on those two at 57 now but school takes priority.)
<br />

<br />
Tenosh on Prexus.</span></td>
